{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_09_03",
  "title": "成宮すず",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――次の日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1400,
          "startTime": 1.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "お、お疲れ様ですわ。今日は……そ、その\n打ち合わせの続き、でした、わよね……？",
      "startTime": 8.0216849773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（先日の一件以来、すっかりヤバい人認定されて）\n（しまったみたいだな……。早く弁明しないと）",
      "startTime": 15.0666667064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すず、やっと分かったんだよ\nどうやら俺達はずっとすれ違ってたみたいだ",
      "startTime": 21.6329922453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "すれ違い……？　どういうことですの？",
      "startTime": 24.9333333731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなから聞いたんだよ。「すずがバレンタイン\nチョコのCMに出演するんだと喜んでいた」ってな",
      "startTime": 32.0000000398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "何も間違っていませんわよね？\nそれの何がおかしいんですの？",
      "startTime": 38.8702538628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタイン時期に放映されるとは言ったけど\nチョコのCMとは言ってないぞ",
      "startTime": 44.3644671105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "え",
      "startTime": 47.0333303213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ポテトチップスのCMだって説明しただろ？\nどうやら浮かれて聞いてなかったみたいだな",
      "startTime": 51.8047775682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな……私、ずっと……\nチョコのCMだと勘違いを……？",
      "startTime": 60.4999990225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "あら……？　ま、待ってくださいまし。勘違いだった\nということは、先日のただれた一件は……！？",
      "startTime": 69.2333323558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ただれた一件って……。ポテトチップスを二枚重ねて\nアヒルの口みたいにする遊びのことを言ったんだよ",
      "startTime": 78.4464446791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ……なるほど……\nそれなら確かに、小学生もやりそうですわね……",
      "startTime": 85.033329304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "お、おい、すず？　どうした？\nそんな虚ろな目をして……",
      "startTime": 93.033329304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "今までの私の言動の数々を思い出して悶絶している\nだけなので、気にしないでくださいまし……",
      "startTime": 99.872406492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……やっと落ち着きましたわ\nご迷惑をおかけして申し訳ありませんでした",
      "startTime": 110.2341861874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、みんなの誤解を解くのは大変だったけどな\n特に沙季は物凄く冷たい目をしてたからな……",
      "startTime": 118.9666626374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ、CM内容の勘違いに気付かなかった俺も\n悪かった。やっぱりチョコのCMの方が良かったか？",
      "startTime": 125.833329304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなことはありませんわ！\n確かに驚きはしましたが……",
      "startTime": 133.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "大好きなポテトチップスのお仕事なんですもの\n嬉しいに決まっていますわ！",
      "startTime": 140.2867232645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "良かった。俺ももともと、すずのためにあるような\n企画だと思ってたからな。期待してるよ",
      "startTime": 146.204401344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "お任せなさい！　ここからは気持ちを切り替えて……\nばっちり決めてみせますわよ！",
      "startTime": 155.1000010569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM撮影当日",
      "startTime": 158.6333338816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.7533308346
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.7533308346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "ポーズはこれで……あとは決め台詞ですわね",
      "startTime": 160.6000076691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "「食べたら……羽ばたけますわよ？\n天使のポテトチップス、新発売！」",
      "startTime": 169.1666667063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "……オーケーですか？　ありがとうございます！\nえ、何か別パターンをアドリブで？",
      "startTime": 177.2333221832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.7833287953
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.0333287953
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわね、それなら……",
      "startTime": 183.8333287953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.2333287953
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "「食べちゃダメと言われるほど\n美味しくなるのは……なぜなんでしょうね？」",
      "startTime": 190.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 194.7000005482
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.4666606027
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "……これも一発オーケーですの？\nやりましたわ、さすが天才・成宮すずですわね！",
      "startTime": 197.4666606027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.0000005482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "すずの好物のCMだけあって、ずっと生き生きしてるな\n……アドリブの台詞は沙季に怒られそうだけど",
      "startTime": 208.188374061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM放送開始後",
      "startTime": 212.4333338815,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.658997599984,
          "startTime": 213.7999928791
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 213.5933247167
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n私のCMはもうご覧になりましたか？",
      "startTime": 215.9752730702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだよ。すずのアドリブの台詞も\nしっかり採用されてたな",
      "startTime": 222.4816673357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですわね。それはまぁ、私考案の\n台詞ですから当然と言えば当然ですが……",
      "startTime": 229.9626042264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ん、どうしたんだ？　すず\nそんなにもじもじして",
      "startTime": 237.3999939361,
